seligi-h, dulang-a and dulang-b. first oil was produced from the angsi-b platform and the larut, lawang/langat and serudon fields in 2002. development projects are currently in progress at bintang, irong barat-b&c, tapis-f, guntong-e, f&g,
raya-b and angsi-c&e.
